```java
rule "Send Voice Message and Control TV on Thursday"
when
    Item SendVoiceMessage changed to ON
then
    val now = new DateTimeType(nav())
    if (now.getHourOfDay() >= 0 && now.getHourOfDay() < 24 && now.getDayOfWeek().getAsText().equals("Thursday")) {
        sendCommand(TV_Item, ON)
    }
end
```